PACO Expression editor


This is an Inkscape extension allowing to produce XBM bitmaps suitable to be displayed on an e-ink or lcd screen
driven by a micro-controller.

Dependencies
------------

For running this extension you need a recent version of Inkscape and Imagemagick

You also need the Python Wand module (optional)

Configuration
-------------

Please also edit the paco-expression.py file to suit paths in your system.
You can disable the Wand module setting USE_WAND=False in the first lines.

